ŚIn loving, everlasting memory of
Eden Harman Bernardy
"Love each other. Be kind to each other. Respect each other
And whenever you can, as much as you can,
LAUGH, DANCE, SING, & CELEBRATE LIFE"
Eden. your spirit lives within and around us. We love you
Beyond measure. Beyond words. ALWAYS"Ž
